OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773338768
OL,3,CShell boss sees pay jump almost 60% to
OL,4,C#13.8m despite profit fall
OL,6,FThe boss of Shell saw his pay package
OL,7,Fjump to #13.8 million for the past
OL,8,Fyear despite delivering lower profits
OL,9,Fat the oil giant.
OL,11,FIt came as the company outlined
OL,12,Fproposals to revamp its executive pay
OL,13,Fpolicy, in a move which would enable
OL,14,Fits boss to receive even larger
OL,15,Fbonuses in future years.
OL,17,FThe FTSE 100 firm's annual report
OL,18,Fshowed chief executive Wael Sawan saw
OL,19,Fhis total pay deal rise for 2025 by
OL,20,Falmost 60% compared with the previous
OL,21,Fyear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773338768
OL,3,CShell boss sees pay jump almost 60% to
OL,4,C#13.8m despite profit fall
OL,6,FHe received #1.9 million in his fixed
OL,7,Fsalary, pension, and benefits for the
OL,8,Fyear, but saw this heavily eclipsed by
OL,9,Faround #11.8 million of bonuses.
OL,11,FThis included a #2.7 million bonus for
OL,12,Fthe year and a #9.1 million share
OL,13,Faward linked to longer-term targets.
OL,15,FIt represents the first year that Mr
OL,16,FSawan could receive a full pay package
OL,17,Fbecause of the three-year vesting
OL,18,Fperiod for his long-term share awards.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773338768
OL,3,CShell boss sees pay jump almost 60% to
OL,4,C#13.8m despite profit fall
OL,6,FThe group's finance boss, Sinead
OL,7,FGorman, saw her total pay deal jump to
OL,8,F#8.5 million for 2025 from #7.25
OL,9,Fmillion a year earlier.
OL,11,FThe higher total pay deals came
OL,12,Fdespite Shell reporting a worse-than-
OL,13,Fexpected 22% plunge in annual profits
OL,14,Flast year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
