OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773338768
OL,3,CShell boss sees pay jump almost 60% to
OL,4,C#13.8m despite profit fall
OL,6,FLast month, the oil firm said
OL,7,Funderlying earnings ` which strips out
OL,8,Fsome commodity-price adjustments and
OL,9,Fone-off charges ` dropped to 18.53
OL,10,Fbillion US dollars (#13.6 billion) for
OL,11,F2025 after a 40% plunge quarter-on-
OL,12,Fquarter in the final three months of
OL,13,Fthe year.
OL,15,FNevertheless, shares in the company
OL,16,Fhave risen by more than 26% over the
OL,17,Fpast year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
