OL,3,CShell boss sees pay jump almost 60% to
OL,4,C#13.8m despite profit fall
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThis includes a roughly 12% rise over
OL,12,Fthe past month, with the group among
OL,13,Fenergy firms to have benefited from a
OL,14,Fjump in oil and gas prices driven by
OL,15,Fthe conflict between Iranian and US-
OL,16,FIsraeli forces.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
