FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773338768
OL,3,CShell boss sees pay jump almost 60% to
OL,4,C#13.8m despite profit fall
OL,6,FShell stressed that the overall pay
OL,7,Fdeal is "commensurate with his
OL,8,Fposition at a major global energy
OL,9,Fcompany and one of the FTSE's largest
OL,10,Fcompanies".
OL,12,FAndrew Speke, interim director of the
OL,13,FHigh Pay Centre, said: "As consumers
OL,14,Fface rising energy and fuel costs,
OL,15,Fthis news will be deeply unpopular.
OL,17,F"The substantial pay rise for Shell's
OL,18,FCEO appears to be part of a wider
OL,19,Fpattern in which leading FTSE 100
OL,20,Fcompanies are showing much less
OL,21,Frestraint in executive remuneration.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773338768
OL,3,CShell boss sees pay jump almost 60% to
OL,4,C#13.8m despite profit fall
OL,6,F"In the City, higher pay is often
OL,7,Fjustified as necessary to compete with
OL,8,FUS counterparts, while there is little
OL,9,Fsign that the Government intends to
OL,10,Fchallenge this trend."
OL,12,FThe company has also outlined
OL,13,Fproposals to change its pay policy for
OL,14,Fexecutives, which shareholders will
OL,15,Fvote on at its annual general meeting
OL,16,Fin May.
OL,18,FThe new policy will allow for a
OL,19,Fpotential 50% increase in the long-
OL,20,Fterm bonus that Mr Sawan could receive
OL,21,Fas chief executive.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773338768
OL,3,CShell boss sees pay jump almost 60% to
OL,4,C#13.8m despite profit fall
OL,6,FHe would now be able to receive a long-
OL,7,Fterm stock award worth up to nine
OL,8,Ftimes his #1.53 million salary,
OL,9,Fmeaning it could reach as high as
OL,10,F#13.8 million if certain performance
OL,11,Fmeasures are hit and the move is
OL,12,Fapproved by shareholders.
OL,14,FThis would relate to long-term awards,
OL,15,Fwhich take three years to vest.
OL,17,FA Shell spokesman said: "Every three
OL,18,Fyears, Shell seeks shareholder
OL,19,Fapproval for a new executive director
OL,20,Fremuneration policy as a standard part
OL,21,Fof regulations for UK-listed companies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773338768
OL,3,CShell boss sees pay jump almost 60% to
OL,4,C#13.8m despite profit fall
OL,6,F"The last vote was in 2023, so this is
OL,7,Fpart of the usual cycle.
OL,9,F"The proposals have been published in
OL,10,Fthe 2025 annual report today and will
OL,11,Fbe voted on at the AGM (annual general
OL,12,Fmeeting)."
